Package: cdmAcm0012
Title: Implementation of CDM Large-Scale Methodology ACM0012
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(person(given = "Christiaan", family = "Pauw", email = "christiaan.pauw@gmal.com", role = c("aut", "cre")))
Description: Provides tidyverse-aligned tooling to implement the Clean Development Mechanism
    large-scale methodology ACM0012 "Waste energy recovery". Functions translate
    numbered equations, applicability conditions, and calculation workflows into reproducible R
    code and include simulation utilities for demonstration and testing purposes tailored to
    waste heat, waste gas, and waste pressure recovery systems.
